{
  "stem": "747.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That why did they bring the sick people?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They can't go to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So anyhow, it wasn't much time to think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were all boarded in the, in a cattle wagon, cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "About 80, 85 people to a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Two containers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One for drinking water, and the other one for toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody hung up a little-- something, had a blanket that they should have a little bit of privacy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And were were sitting on the floor, a loaf of bread for everyone, and then the train started to roll.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we arrived to the Czech-Hungarian border, Nazis took over from the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a big speech in German, that if you're going to work, then we will-- we helped to win the war, then we can hope that we will survive.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the-- they let us go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the blessing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the train was rolling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we-- the second day, we arrived to the Polish border, my father said-- somebody had a map with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they looked at it, and said, we are not going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're taking us to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's not good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but we couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were closed in like animals in a-- there was a little window in the top, chicken wire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't-- and the kids were dying from thirst.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Crying, and fighting, and miserable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was two days and a night, we traveled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was a bright, sunny day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we heard that in Poland, a lot of others-- a lot of bad things happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we knew that Poland is a killing field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew that people who were out-- went-- were taken out, they never returned.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
